            212 => 
            array (
                'id' => 223,
                'category_id' => 6,
                'category_code' => '0101002',
                'user_type' => 1,
                'title' => '测试公告',
            'content' => '<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">原标题：创新不足，亮点不多的2018苹果发布会，真的不用熬夜看了</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://p0.ifengimg.com/pmop/2018/0913/27A3BF46FB9423A43DCE1A615C3DB64B906708B8_size624_w2302_h1080.png" alt=""/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">随着指针转动到北京时间凌晨一点，我们熟悉的老朋友，全世界人民的“厨子”——蒂姆库克，操着一向沉稳的语速开始了今年秋季的发布会……然而在发布会开始之前，这一届发布会的信息已经被泄漏个“底儿掉”，这样的发布会已经成为了一场“验证会”。那么参照标准答案，看看你们都猜对了那些产品？</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">新表换旧表，外观终于有变化了</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">这一次，Apple Watch 终于在外观上有了变化，尺寸也从之前的 38mm 和 42mm 屏幕，提升到了 40mm 和 44mm 的尺寸，屏占比分别提升了 35% 和 32%。同时，也更新了各种动态壁纸，以能显示多个时区的壁纸，对于商旅人士很有作用：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://p0.ifengimg.com/pmop/2018/0913/F98CE8798F51428D6AC07D13E8DFE3823047506F_size76_w629_h383.jpeg" alt="Apple Watch Series 4"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Apple Watch Series 4</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">当然，除了外观上的改变，Apple Watch Series 4 也更响了（扬声器音量提升 50%），速度更快了（采用了 S4 处理器，64 位双核处理器，速度是 Series 3 的两倍）。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">不过，这其中最实用的还是 Apple Watch Series 4 上的心率监测功能：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">低心率监测（是的，低心率不一定健康）；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">常驻后台的心率监测，能够检测到心房震颤，可以监测意外跌倒等等；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">它支持显示心电图（ECG）整个采集过程仅需要 30 秒。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">苹果为了更准确地监测用户是否意外跌倒，还是开发了一套算法：比如，真正的意外跌倒，是身体前倾，手臂后摆的。针对不同种类的跌落姿势，都设置了判定标准。此外，Apple Watch Series 4 的 ECG 是需要额外硬件才能实现的，并且它还达到了 America Heart Association 和 FDA 的认证。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://p0.ifengimg.com/pmop/2018/0913/022CB53EBE6FFCE00192863C991D7023DF107635_size813_w1440_h1080.png" alt="Apple Watch Series 4"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Apple Watch Series 4</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">换而言之，Apple Watch Series 4 的用户可以拿着打印出来的心率图变化去看病了。现在苹果已经把 Apple Watch 当成了专业的医疗辅助工具了。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">苹果方面还表示，虽然功能增加了，性能变强了，屏幕变大了，但 Apple Watch Series 4 依然能做到 18 小时的正常使用续航以及 6 小时 GPS 模式下的续航。同时这一代 Apple Watch 依然分为基础版和数据版，售价为 399 美元以及 499 美元。具体上市日期为 9 月 21 日。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">最让人兴奋的，依旧是上一代 Apple Watch 的降价，起步价调整到了 279 美元——另外，如果想要试试新表功能的用户，可以在 9 月 17 日更新 watchOS 5 尝尝鲜。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">iPhone Xs：双卡双待安排上了</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">手表介绍完了，终于到了整个发布会的主角新一代 iPhone Xs。关于这一代 iPhone Xs，其实媒体曝光的差不多了。比如外观设计没有太大变化，加入了新配色（金色），性能得到了提升。性能提升成为了介绍这一代产品的重头戏。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://p0.ifengimg.com/pmop/2018/0913/53860FE6F1213C5CD0D1B857E6045F06670A4E01_size91_w1024_h768.jpeg" alt="新 iPhone 系列图"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">新 iPhone 系列图</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">整个 iPhone Xs 发布环节几乎有一半都是在介绍 7nm A12 Bionic 芯片性能如何强大。比如打游戏画面更清晰，照片处理速度更快，人像模式支持景深调节——大部分的人像模式，使用的女性模特都是黑人女性，不得不说，苹果的求生欲还是很强的。毕竟追求真实是苹果拍照的一向风格。自动美颜？不存在的。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">此外，iPhone Xs 由过去的 IP67 级别的防水防尘，升级到了 IP68 级。用苹果的原话说，就是你可以让手机先在池塘里躺上半小时，再决定要不要捞起来。不过，笔者关心的不是新手机的性能和防护表现，而是散热。上一代产品 iPhone X 离开了空调房，夏天打游戏卡顿也不是一天两天的事情了。IP68 级防水防尘可能是苹果给予游戏玩家降温的新思路。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://p0.ifengimg.com/pmop/2018/0913/A9A3006D90EAAE5DE6458EE19FE95183C4C9D948_size692_w1440_h1080.png" alt="A12 Bionic"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">A12 Bionic</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">屏幕依旧是顶级的 OLED 屏幕，支持 120hz 屏幕触摸刷新率，支持 3D Touch，但并不支持 Apple Pencil。最为关键的是，这一代手机屏幕大小并不只有 5.8 英寸可选，还有一台 iPhone Xs Max。如同名称所暗示的，这是一款“大”手机。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://p0.ifengimg.com/pmop/2018/0913/C2900236B6BE526BE054929D5D2BAD5A84493946_size708_w1440_h1080.png" alt="iPhone Xs 系列相机"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">iPhone Xs 系列相机</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Max 的意思既指大屏幕，也指大电池，它在 iPhone 8 Plus 大小的机身里塞入了一块 6.5 英寸的手机屏幕。同时它支持分屏应用功能，横置手机即可激活。一样机身大小的手机，如果砸到了脸上，后果都是一样的。不过它与 iPhone 8 Plus 一样，砸到脸上会非常疼。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://p0.ifengimg.com/pmop/2018/0913/D55E6CFDAF99B6F26C3027CBF35AEF779FFAEF05_size700_w1440_h1080.png" alt="iPhone Xs 系列-镜头"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">iPhone Xs 系列-镜头</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">如果以上这两个产品在这些方面没办法打动你，那么笔者相信，接下来的设计一定会让你纠结半天：iPhone Xs 终于全线支持双卡双待，并且针对中国还推出了定制版的 iPhone Xs 双卡卡槽。其他国家地区虽然也支持双卡双待，但他们大多都是 eSIM 实现双卡双待的功能。由此可以看出，苹果对于中国用户的重视程度。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://p0.ifengimg.com/pmop/2018/0913/AB4595A2F46CA67A7A6E012EC19BBE9BF2386084_size808_w1440_h1080.png" alt=""/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Face ID on iPhone Xs</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">另外一个可能会诱发你剁手的原因大概就是 iPhone Xs 续航时间要比 iPhone 8 Plus 长半小时，而 iPhone Xs Max 续航时间长一个半小时。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">至此，你也看出了今年的 iPhone Xs 系列产品，看得见的创新显然不如去年。总结起来就是，性能，双卡，大电池——苹果终于挤完了牙膏，中国用户期待的功能已经上线完毕了。如果硬要给买 iPhone Xs Max 另外的理由，我觉得可能是因为金色配色辨识度比较高吧。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">One More iPhone and No More Air…</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">尽管今年库克并没有宣布任何 One More Thing，但我们姑且还是把 iPhone XR 算作吧。毕竟，它是最后一个出场的硬件：成本更低的 6.1 英寸 LCD 屏幕，7 系铝合金中框，单摄像头设计，IP67 级防水，其余的参数与 iPhone Xs 系列产品没有太大的差别。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://p0.ifengimg.com/pmop/2018/0913/F188F5680748ECA8E8133D1B0DDD8CB086DC648D_size840_w1440_h1080.png" alt="iPhone XR"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">iPhone XR</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">如果还是找不同，那可能就是 iPhone XR 更多彩——它拥有红、黄、白、珊瑚色、黑以及蓝六种配色。用户花了最少的钱，买到了最多彩的手机，同时由于手机采用了铝中框，可能手机很更轻一些。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">那么问题来了，iPhone XR 中的这个 R 到底是什么意思呢？笔者认为，r is for re-design。也就是苹果把 iPhone Xs 系列的产品，在 ID 设计上做出了重新的调整，比如改个尺寸，让它处于大小两款产品之间；重新给 iPhone Xs 系列产品，换多种颜色……</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">但是实际上，仔细观察苹果官网，会发现红色的产品下方的标注了 Product RED™ 的符号。这个红色，其实是苹果公司与“红计划（Product RED）”的一次长期合作，目的是呼吁为非洲的艾滋病预防项目筹集资金，提升公众的防病意识。这些特殊产品销售而产生的利润，将会有 1% 赠与公益事业项目。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://p0.ifengimg.com/pmop/2018/0913/32BF69543C3B7A586970C71AA9D709CAA4F896CA_size1961_w2746_h1080.png" alt="iPhone XR-多彩机身"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">iPhone XR-多彩机身</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">发布会到这里基本接近尾声，蒂姆库克上台，提到了 HomePod 更新支持了 AirPlay2，能够将两台 HomePod 连接成为立体声系统。接着，他扶了扶眼镜，仓促地又宣布了 Mac 新系统 Mojave 的更新时间，然后，就没有然后了。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">从去年跳票至今的 AirPower 并没有登场，支持无线充电的 AirPods 充电盒没有亮相，MacBook Air 的产品依旧没有更新，更不用提 Mac Mini 和 iPad Pro 了。这一场发布会没有任何“Air”产品。可能大量的读者猜中了发布会的开头，并没有猜到这结尾。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://p0.ifengimg.com/pmop/2018/0913/407164FF0BDF9C91A0BAC3A0DB4793A55C31C0D9_size961_w1440_h1080.png" alt="iPhone Xs iPhone XR 售价"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">iPhone Xs iPhone XR 售价</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">最后，让我们看看 iPhone Xs 系列产品与 iPhone XR 的售价：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">iPhone XR 售价：64GB 为 6499 元、128GB 为 6999 元、256GB 为 7899 元；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">iPhone Xs 售价：64GB 卖 8699 元、256GB 卖 10099 元、512GB 为 11899 元；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">iPhone Xs Max 售价：64GB 为 9599 元、256GB 为 10999 元、512GB 为 12799 元。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">iPhone Xs 系列产品现在已经开放预订了，而 iPhone XR 系列产品最早要到 10 月 19 日开售。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: simsun, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">这是一场创新不足，亮点不多的发布会，手表多了心率功能，手机出了双卡双待，摄像头多了可调节的背景虚化功能，就连电池续航多了那么点时间也值得拿出来炫耀了？倒是多了几种漂亮颜色的iPhone XR让人眼前一亮。除了这次发布了7纳米的A12芯片让人看到了苹果还在孜孜不倦的提升性能，你真看不出来新发布的iPhone产品和国产手机旗舰机有多大的差别。也许2018年，会成为苹果iPhone的转折之年。</p><p><br/></p>',
